commit.message:
pa.md (movqi, [...]): Discourage regclass from preferring anything which involves a FP<->GR copy.

	* pa.md (movqi, movhi, movsi, movdi, movsf, movdf): Discourage
	regclass from preferring anything which involves a FP<->GR copy.

From-SVN: r3123
